Package: singR
Type: Package
Title: Simultaneous Non-Gaussian Component Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2022-07-28
Author: Liangkang Wang [aut, cre] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3393-243X>),
  Irina Gaynanova [aut] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4116-0268>),
